<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="today-adv">today <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tə'deɪ/    美 /tə'deɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在今天；现在；当代：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you going shopping today? 
你今天要去购物吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>More women have jobs today than in the past. 
现在就业的妇女比以前多了。</p></div></div>